data.title: Lavilash Lashes
data.meta_description: Lavilash Lashes is dedicated to provide professional individual and volume Lash Extensions by Licensed Lash Technicians. Our services will provide a natural beauty enhancement for each client.

Are your natural lashes not curly or dark enough? Try our Lash Lift and Tint! Made to curl and darken your lashes for about 4 weeks before returning for another appointment.

​

Lash Lift + Tint $95

Need your natural lashes laminated into a style? We will shape your natural brows you that will stay put for about 4 weeks until you next appointment.

​

Eyebrow Lamination $85

Are your natural lashes long enough but not curly or dark enough? Try our Lash Lift and Tint! Made to curl and darken your lashes for about 4 weeks before returning for another appointment.

​

Lash Lift + Tint $95

Would you like to have your extensions removed? Schedule a removal and we will completely remove your extensions and leave you with your natural lashes!

First time receiving Lash extensions? Are you highly sensitive to adhesives? Or just have questions and would like a preview on the lashing process? Schedule a patch test! You will receive a few extensions on the corner of one eye to ensure there is no allergic reaction within 24hrs. You may book your patch test and full set within 24 hours of each other.

​

Patch Test: Free

Looking for an extra razzle dazzle? Add color lashes to your Full set or Fill! You may get a section completed or spikes across your eyes! Just let your lash tech know that you're interested at your appointment!

​

Cost: +$10

​

Colors: Red, Pink, Green, Blue, Purple
